        "description": "<html>\n <head>\n </head>\n <body>\n  Welcome to Suburbia, just outside the City, sometime in <i>198X</i>. This is the journey of Kid, a teenager stuck between the limitations of innocent youth and the obligations of inevitable adulthood. The story unfolds when Kid discovers the local arcade – finding new worlds, and new meaning, in video games. For every visit to the arcade – every game uncovered, every move mastered, every demon defeated – Kid grows stronger. And the lines between game and reality starts to blur…\n  <br>\n  <br>\n  This is <i>198X</i> – where a new life is just 1 credit away.\n  <br>\n  <br>\n  Estimated play time: 2 hours\n </body>\n</html>",
