        "description": "<html>\n <head>\n </head>\n <body>\n  <img height=\"139\" src=\"https://hb.imgix.net/2756ba98ad3bbc45a3b0c7b71f03ada00ea71c98.jpg?auto=compress,format&s=b7ef9ed738e1b47918b88ad077be7dda\" width=\"600\">\n  <br>\n  <br>\n  From the makers of Heavenly Sword, Enslaved: Odyssey to the West, and DmC: Devil May Cry, comes a warrior’s brutal journey into myth and madness.\n  <br>\n  <br>\n  Set in the Viking age, a broken Celtic warrior embarks on a haunting vision quest into Viking Hell to fight for the soul of her dead lover.\n  <br>\n  <br>\n  Created in collaboration with neuroscientists and people who experience psychosis, Hellblade: Senua’s Sacrifice will pull you deep into Senua’s mind.\n  <br>\n  <br>\n  <img height=\"107\" src=\"https://hb.imgix.net/bb59cd090e5e905cc3a570a9845e5da111c97241.jpg?auto=compress,format&s=5edbba9f3567d36172692a56d5e85278\" width=\"600\">\n  <br>\n  <br>\n  <img height=\"338\" src=\"https://hb.imgix.net/825ae2929a2ca99c90f19f9ff7a2db0e3b9ec356.jpg?auto=compress,format&s=f17f7ffa37d17873eef0a82fa57dc848\" width=\"600\">\n </body>\n</html>",
