        "humble_type": "initial",
        "title": "Verlet Swing",
        "description": "<html>\n <head>\n </head>\n <body>\n  <img height=\"94\" src=\"https://hb.imgix.net/22ba18bad1294c04eb32ab6ded48cdb6e3251da6.png?auto=compress,format&s=8168807010aeed00d3bedc787793a522\" width=\"620\">\n  <br>\n  <img src=\"https://steamcdn-a.akamaihd.net/steam/apps/811870/extras/VS_620x349.png?t=1568883051\">\n  <br>\n  Everyone has had a fever dream. Weird stuff happens. Sometimes you find yourself in an eccentric world where statues keep staring you down while you die on impact with any of your surroundings. Armed with a hookshot you must swing for your life into these glowing spheres, only to find yourself being teleported into a different, but similar world with more difficult obstacles. That’s basically <i>Verlet Swing</i>, a game that may or may not have been concocted during a fever dream.\n  <br>\n  <br>\n  <img height=\"47\" src=\"https://hb.imgix.net/e0e083a4dfedd442cfae5844e866f44dafea9136.png?auto=compress,format&s=f326136f597a12709f74746d2a20f8d3\" width=\"620\">\n  <br>\n  <ul>\n   <li>\n    100 levels of fast-paced swinging action!\n    <br>\n   </li>\n   <li>\n    Challenge modes!\n    <br>\n   </li>\n   <li>\n    Global, friend and Twitch leaderboards!\n    <br>\n   </li>\n   <li>\n    Increasingly difficult gameplay. The final levels are only for the best of swingers!\n    <br>\n   </li>\n   <li>\n    Create, share and play levels with the Steam Workshop.\n    <br>\n   </li>\n   <li>\n    Twitch stream integration!\n   </li>\n  </ul>\n </body>\n</html>",
