        "description": "<i>A Case of Distrust</i> is a narrative mystery from 1924 San Francisco. Play as private investigator Phyllis Cadence Malone in this historical 2D adventure game. Explore underground speakeasies, smoke-filled billiard halls, classic barber shops, and more. Catch suspects in lies by using evidence, statements, and your wits. Intrinsic challenges face our heroine, as she struggles against a pushback on emancipation, leading to many doubts, both internal and external. Uncover the truth in a mystery full of deception!\n<strong class=\"hmb\">\n <br>\n <br>\n Features\n</strong>\n<br>\n<ul>\n <li>\n  A hardboiled mystery, working past deceptive characters towards the truth\n  <br>\n </li>\n <li>\n  1924 San Francisco with historically accurate details\n  <br>\n </li>\n <li>\n  Saul Bass inspired visuals and scene transitions\n  <br>\n </li>\n <li>\n  Finger-snapping music that gives style to the roaring 20s\n  <br>\n </li>\n <li>\n  Themes of poverty, racism, and emancipation that tie into contemporary issues\n </li>\n</ul>",
