        "title": "Automachef",
        "description": "<html>\n <head>\n </head>\n <body>\n  Welcome to <i>Automachef</i>, a resource management puzzler where you design kitchens, program machinery and watch your genius come to life! It’s time to engineer tomorrow’s kitchens, today!\n  <strong class=\"hmb\">\n   <br>\n   <br>\n   Plan. Position. Program:\n  </strong>\n  <br>\n  Design and build automated restaurants, then program them to run like well-oiled machines! Do you have a can-do attitude and the know-how to conquer the world of automated restaurants?\n  <br>\n  <br>\n  <video autoplay=\"autoplay\" loop=\"loop\" muted=\"muted\" preload=\"auto\" style=\"width: 600px; height: 252px;\">\n   <source src=\"https://hb.imgix.net/e36ad440b7e638f394840cd9df6d36f56b08051f.gif?auto=format&fm=mp4&s=77fd78a6894e8204f888dfc1775960c0\" type=\"video/mp4\">\n   </source>\n  </video>\n  <strong class=\"hmb\">\n   <br>\n   <br>\n   Challenging Puzzles:\n  </strong>\n  <br>\n  Fine tune your mind as you tackle intricate spatial, resource management and scenario puzzles! Not enough hot dogs? You’ll sort it! Kitchens on fire? No problem for a smart human like you!\n  <br>\n  <br>\n  <video autoplay=\"autoplay\" loop=\"loop\" muted=\"muted\" preload=\"auto\" style=\"width: 600px; height: 252px;\">\n   <source src=\"https://hb.imgix.net/bce7e096178d548378a879e7aa8e0d0152801a3d.gif?auto=format&fm=mp4&s=477fbadde4441ea55598072789fc69f0\" type=\"video/mp4\">\n   </source>\n  </video>\n  <strong class=\"hmb\">\n   <br>\n   <br>\n   Multiple Brain-Tickling Modes:\n  </strong>\n  <br>\n  Take on the campaign levels, traverse your way through the business world in contracts mode, or just go nuts and bolts in the sandbox test mode and play until you get your fill!\n  <br>\n  <br>\n  <video autoplay=\"autoplay\" loop=\"loop\" muted=\"muted\" preload=\"auto\" style=\"width: 600px; height: 252px;\">\n   <source src=\"https://hb.imgix.net/69ef5a28d4f13e63ae8b055e2dd95355997fa1d3.gif?auto=format&fm=mp4&s=fe5d4e5fe846b4903547e5dcb9622c5f\" type=\"video/mp4\">\n   </source>\n  </video>\n  <strong class=\"hmb\">\n   <br>\n   <br>\n   Endless Charm and Quirky Humour:\n  </strong>\n  <br>\n  All delivered in an abundance by our helplessly misguided human protagonist- Robert Person. Who is definitely a human. Don’t ask questions.\n  <br>\n  <br>\n  <video autoplay=\"autoplay\" loop=\"loop\" muted=\"muted\" preload=\"auto\" style=\"width: 600px; height: 245px;\">\n   <source src=\"https://hb.imgix.net/32b6629a7bc47ac5feea42388718a943d1857a40.gif?auto=format&fm=mp4&s=477d02095f3dba0e9f2ea8a4063da7a2\" type=\"video/mp4\">\n   </source>\n  </video>\n  <strong class=\"hmb\">\n   <br>\n   <br>\n   Mod Support:\n  </strong>\n  <br>\n  Think you could bring some more pizazz to the table? GREAT! Step on up to the plate and create your own ingredients, recipes and scenario levels via Steam Workshop!\n  <br>\n  <br>\n  <video autoplay=\"autoplay\" loop=\"loop\" muted=\"muted\" preload=\"auto\" style=\"width: 600px; height: 245px;\">\n   <source src=\"https://hb.imgix.net/f03be19a5bf9025b3bc63d9f22a6d60e7fb0c19b.gif?auto=format&fm=mp4&s=bb7ad4aa8e00bd511c21c0b8cd1e39e6\" type=\"video/mp4\">\n   </source>\n  </video>\n </body>\n</html>",
