        "description": "<img height=\"346\" src=\"https://hb.imgix.net/5760865728fe7892e40b2f18804e153ef9111d4a.png?auto=compress,format&s=9e69ca1bf67e3778a31bfd536973cf25\" width=\"616\">\n<strong class=\"hmb\">\n <br>\n <br>\n Be the Zombie. Kick A** and Take Brains\n</strong>\n<br>\nIt’s 1959 and the city of Punchbowl, PA, is a beacon of progress and ideal living. Show the living that law and order are no match for a dead man on a mission. Your boyfriend’s back Maggie, and Punchbowl is gonna be in trouble!\n<br>\n<img height=\"346\" src=\"https://hb.imgix.net/c0d476dc2b2a69ea3cb6c70990e3e286f7cc5f50.png?auto=compress,format&s=fe9e6d658fd6d2caf97a8b20bbc7e19d\" width=\"616\">\n<strong class=\"hmb\">\n <br>\n <br>\n Eat Brains\n</strong>\n<br>\nChomp on the living and replenish your bodily arsenal of: zombie sputum, gut grenades, and the stunning unholy flatulence\n<br>\n<img height=\"346\" src=\"https://hb.imgix.net/41d460e319d5f35c6bf452701d31f01049231df1.png?auto=compress,format&s=b6be645dba7173b8079eef27d9152668\" width=\"616\">\n<strong class=\"hmb\">\n <br>\n <br>\n Possess Punchbowl’s Population\n</strong>\n<br>\nClamp your severed hand to a barbershop quartet singer’s head and raygun away\n<br>\n<img height=\"346\" src=\"https://hb.imgix.net/dde62378ecfc0893b297785c76918a3091381380.png?auto=compress,format&s=22e7b20c51f21a4680454f21386fd2c4\" width=\"616\">\n<strong class=\"hmb\">\n <br>\n <br>\n Build Your Zombie Horde\n</strong>\n<br>\nConvert your enemies into undead allies & lead a zombie assault on the living\n<br>\n<img height=\"346\" src=\"https://hb.imgix.net/1398283df6428f8b7cca63f13d5dffba15ae708d.png?auto=compress,format&s=208d0483977051d7c940290c6715fad9\" width=\"616\">\n<strong class=\"hmb\">\n <br>\n <br>\n Bring Civilization to its Knees\n</strong>\n<br>\nShow the retro-futuristic city of Punchbowl, PA that they can’t escape the past\n<br>\n<img height=\"346\" src=\"https://hb.imgix.net/5a35e6b3e1a91a333bd810c10e3110d435140c27.png?auto=compress,format&s=ccb0d3ff3d988c0ec3b66c600f30c708\" width=\"616\">\n<strong class=\"hmb\">\n <br>\n <br>\n Stubbs and Chill\n</strong>\n<br>\nInvite a friend to play as Grubbs for classic couch cooperative hijinks. (Friend not included)\n",
