        "description": "Explore the dark hallways of underground parking and find a passage to the hidden obscure underworld. Find new weapons and use them to survive. Solve the mystery of this cursed place and the monsters that inhabit it.\n<div></div>\n<div></div>\n<div><img height=\"139\" src=\"https://hb.imgix.net/c417e334c4c9e4a02c78e75919218e23c9ea8136.png?auto=compress,format&amp;s=fb67e9a36aab328eaf7c3f1f52beaa5d\" width=\"616\">\n<ul>\n<li>Every weapon has its dedicated use in a battle against the mutants, the undead, and the military; <br><img height=\"139\" src=\"https://hb.imgix.net/83d660a6952d81c8e7e71efe42386e6b9c8185ec.png?auto=compress,format&amp;s=cf649ee906d87f9aaf464d0065dc7b49\" width=\"616\"> </li>\n<li>Unique gameplay combines survival, ammo management, shoot’em’up, and racing; <br><img height=\"139\" src=\"https://hb.imgix.net/c78ec4b7879298b04f1a591a5b3e64847b3e352d.png?auto=compress,format&amp;s=c9c28bf8f1a3f5fcfbf87a23f860036e\" width=\"616\"> </li>\n<li>Inspired by Splatterpunk storytelling style; <br><img height=\"139\" src=\"https://hb.imgix.net/d527e3f1d8a920a62dfccfea2f76646a36bc8032.png?auto=compress,format&amp;s=1fd9ef29e94fed8cfd60a5720bdae986\" width=\"616\"> </li>\n<li>Levels filled with secrets and challenges.</li>\n</ul>\n</div>",
